<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM12.9">
<l>kūṭṭi liruntu kiḷiyeppōtuṅ kōvintā kōvintā veṉṟaḻaikkum</l>
<l>ūṭṭuk koṭātu ceṟuppaṉāki lulakaḷan tāṉeṉ ṟuyarakkūvum</l>
<l>nāṭṭiṟ ṟalaippaḻi yeytiyuṅkaḷ naṉmai yiḻantu talaiyiṭātē</l>
<l>cūṭṭuyar māṭaṅkaḷ cūḻntutōṉṟun tuvarā patikkeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>At all times, the parakeet calls out, ‘Govinda! Govinda!’ from [its] cage.</l>
<l>If I [show] anger by not feeding [it], it cries loudly, ‘He who measured the worlds!’</l>
<l>Send me to the Dvārakā city which appears surrounded by adorned high mansions</l>
<l>So that you do not lose your good [name]—earning great blame in the land—</l>
<l rend="indent">And hang [your] heads [down]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
